'''''Triangle: Going to America''''' ni filime yo muri [[Etiyopiya]] 2014 yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Theodros Teshome . Yatowe mu byiciro bitatu bitandukanye muri Afurika ya Movie Academy Awards 2015; Filime nziza mundimi nyafurika, Umuyobozi mwiza na Filime nziza. <ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2015/08/see-full-list-of-2015-african-movie-academy-awards-amaa-nominees-oc-ukeje-hilda-dokubo-ini-edo-more/</ref>

Yatsindiye "Igihembo cy'Abashinze Iserukiramuco- Narrative" mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime nyafurika muri 2015 ndetse inegukana "Igihembo cy'abaterankunga" muIserukiramuco rya Sinema rya filimi mu [[Rwanda]]  muri 2015. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/191233</ref>

== Icegeranyo ==
Filime yazengurutse imigabane itatu kandi ivuga ku kibazo cyo kwimukira muri Amerika mu buryo butemewe. Kaleab na Jemal bafite ubushake bwo gukora ibishoboka byose kugirango bagere muri Amerika ubuzima bwiza. Mu rugendo rutoroshye, bahura na Winta nziza (Mahder Assefa), mugenzi wabo wimukira uturutse muri Eritereya. Kaleab na Winta bakundana mugihe bava muri Afrika yuburasirazuba banyuze muri Libiya, Ubutaliyani, Mexico ndetse amaherezo bakerekeza muri Amerika. <ref>https://www.meetup.com/fr-FR/DMV-Black-Film-Media-Club/events/220894302/</ref>

